Class ElectricVehicle

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Thread
com.example.epj2.model.electricvehicle.ElectricVehicle

Direct Known Subclasses:
Bicycle, Car, Scooter
public abstract class ElectricVehicle extends Thread implements Serializable
Represents an electric vehicle. This class provides methods to access and manipulate electric vehicle attributes.
